data.description: This as-is home is a blank slate for you to make it your own. Take a look at the bones of the home along with the level, spacious yard and the large workshop. With some TLC, this home could be made into a great family home. The living room is spacious and open to the kitchen. There are two bedroom located towards the front of the home with a nice- sized full bath. Step back to the partially completed renovation. This primary bedroom could be a beautiful retreat with these high vaulted ceilings. The primary bath has the space needed to make it exactly what you desire. This home will not qualify for FHA or USDA. Be careful when walking on deck. Enjoy the pros that this property offers along with the convenient location. Investors and owner occupants welcome.
